features: HIGH-QUALITY MATERIALS: Protect your documents with our fireproof accordion file organizer.Made of double-layered,non-itchy,silicone-coated fiberglass,it can withstand up to 2000℉ and has passed the SGS Test (UL94 VTM-0 Certified). Highly water-resistant,it's the perfect solution for unexpected spills or accidents.Keep your files organized and easily accessible with our expanding file organizer.Invest in added protection today！

UPGRADED DESIGN: Say goodbye to cluttered files and disorganization with JUNDUN's file organizer folders.Our unique design allows you to neatly store and classify letter/A4 files, receipts, cards, USB drives, pen, passports,and more.With our according file organizer,you only need one organizer to handle all your files,saving you time and money.Simplify your life and stay organized with our cost-effective solution

PLENTY OF ROOM: Our Accordian File Organizer has 13 individual pockets,1 zipper pocket,1 pen slot,6 card slots,4 small mesh bags,4 medium mesh bags,and 1 main pocket,all in a compact size of 13.97"x10.43"x1.96".With ample space,you can securely store all your important documents and other items in this accordian folder while effectively classifying and finding your files

DOUBLE ZIPPER & COLORFUL LABELS: Easily access and organize your files with this expandable file folder organizer.Featuring a double zipper for convenient opening and closing,you won't have to worry about losing any important documents.The included colorful labels make categorizing your files effortless

THE QUALITY MAX PROMISE: JUNDUN cut no corners in our product and will provide you with a high-quality expanding file folder and excellent customer service! We know that you are a big deal,and if there is any quality problem,please don't hesitate to contact us via Amazon.We promise to promptly arrange a replacement or refund if there are any quality issues

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I like it, it’s sturdy and has lots of pockets for little things. It doesn’t expand a ton so no huge packets

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Inside zipper broken
reviews.reviewText: After 2 weeks the inside zipper is already broken. Thankfully the main zipper is still working. It has been helpful to hold our documents during our travel.Edit: I did change my rating from 3 to 5 stars because of the customer service! I don't want a refund since the folder still functions properly and I like how much it holds. It would be nice if the inside zipper works, but it's not a deal breaker for me. I do feel like the outside zipper will last.

reviews.reviewText: Holds quite a few files in it so will help me avoid lugging around a larger accordion file with my clipboard. Will just carry this to job sites now

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Stores the most important documents and it's fire proof.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Has Major Flaw
reviews.reviewText: I bought this organizer to put all my important documents in. It seems nicely constructed and is sturdy. One small thing of note is that it does not open completely flat due to where the zipper stops. That I didn't find to be a huge issue. What I did find to be a deal breaker and cause me to return this item are the card sleeves. They Do Not fit a social security card. They are too narrow. Considering that this is the only type of card I need to store, it made this binder useless to me. If the manufacturer had made these sleeves like a quarter of an inch wider it would have been perfect.
